Measured effect
---------------
Profiling was done with QUIVI_ANIM_PROFILE enabled.

One-file helper baseline:
- GIF sample-512-80.gif: 2.264s total load
  - helper subprocess: 2.097s
  - BMP load into Quivi: 0.099s
  - helper internal work: 0.938812s

- Animated WebP 001_1_1.webp: 3.515s total load
  - helper subprocess: 3.266s
  - BMP load into Quivi: 0.200s
